OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and patchy rain across
OL,6,Fcentral areas continues southwards,
OL,7,Fclearing the UK into the evening.
OL,8,FSunny spells elsewhere, but a few
OL,9,Fshowers over northern Scotland and
OL,10,Feastern coasts of England, where it
OL,11,Fwill be breezy. Below-average
OL,12,Ftemperatures for most.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloud and rain moves
OL,15,Fsoutheast across Scotland and Northern
OL,16,FIreland overnight. Elsewhere, dry with
OL,17,Fclear spells and lighter winds,
OL,18,Fallowing a rural frost to form in
OL,19,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
