OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FRain in the north gradually
OL,6,Fclear south through the day. Sunny
OL,7,Fspells following with scattered
OL,8,Fshowers in the north and northwest.
OL,9,FFeeling chilly, especially in the
OL,10,Fbrisk northerly breeze.
